===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm}}, from {{etyl|ang}} {{term|hleahtor||laughter, jubilation, derision|lang=ang}}, from {{proto|gem-pro|hlahtraz|laughter|lang=en}}, from {{proto|ine-pro|klek-||kleg-|to shout|lang=en}}. Cognate with German {{term|Gelächter||laughter, hilarity, merriment|lang=de}}, Danish and Norwegian  {{term|latter||laughter|lang=da|lang=no}},  Icelandic {{term|hlátur||laughter|lang=is}}. More at {{l|en|laugh}}.

